ðŸ§  Business Case: Trending Product Spike Detection by Time Window

Youâ€™re working with the analytics team of a shopping app. They want to detect products that suddenly got a lot of orders in the past 1 hour, compared to their average order volume per hour over the past day.


---

ðŸ—‚ï¸ Table: orders

order_id	product_id	order_time

1	P1	2024-06-19 09:00:00
2	P1	2024-06-19 10:00:00
